events.name: San Francisco 49ers at Los Angeles Rams

headlines.description: — Everything seemed to indicate the San Francisco 49ers were in for a long night when they traveled south on a short week without Brock Purdy, Nick Bosa, George Kittle and their top three wide receivers to face the surging Los Angeles Rams.
headlines.shortLinkText: Short-handed 49ers stop Rams on downs in overtime, preserving a 26-23 victory

highlights.headline: Colts destroy Raiders at home

highlights.headline: Texans trounce short-handed Ravens on the road
highlights.description: The Texans go on the road and pick up a huge 44-10 win over a short-handed Ravens team.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NFL Highlight (Texans trounce short-handed Ravens on the road) 2025/10/05 ESHEET

headlines.description: — C.J. Stroud threw for 244 yards and four touchdowns, and Houston strolled to a 44-10 win over a depleted Baltimore team Sunday, matching both the most lopsided road win in Texans' history and the most lopsided home loss in Ravens' history.
headlines.shortLinkText: Stroud throws for 4 touchdowns as the Texans blow out the battered Ravens 44-10
